SplitGenerator
-------------
Takes 5 command-line arguments:
url - the path to the dataset file
nrfolds - the number of cross-validation folds
nrrepeats - the number of repeats
destination - the destination path of the split arff file
option - cv or holdout (for cross validation and holdout respectively)

Dependencies:
WEKA

example:
java SplitGenerator data/iris.arff 10 10 desktop cv
